    "where R h i denotes the top i adjectives from the human ranking.",
    "MAP = 1 if, and only if, the top five adjectives from R h 5 have an exact one-to-one correspondence with the top five adjectives from R l, so, unlike AP, it takes the internal ranking of the adjectives into account.",
